sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP TLS
    participant ISCtrl as InferenceService<br/>Reconciler
    participant LLMCtrl as LLMInferenceService<br/>Reconciler
    participant GWCtrl as Gateway<br/>Reconciler
    participant NIMCtrl as NIM Account<br/>Reconciler
    participant CMCtrl as ConfigMap<br/>Reconciler
    participant NVAuth as authn.nvidia.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NVAPI as api.ngc.nvidia.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NVCR as nvcr.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,NVCR: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/443, User Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Review<br/>HTTPS/443, K8s Cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit (mutated)
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

    K8sAPI->>ISCtrl: Watch event: ISVC created
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create KEDA TriggerAuth<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    Note over User,NVCR: Flow 2: NIM Account Provisioning

    User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR<br/>HTTPS/443, User Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate (singleton check)<br/>HTTPS/443, K8s Cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit
    K8sAPI-->>User: Account created

    K8sAPI->>NIMCtrl: Watch event: Account created
    NIMCtrl->>NVAuth: Acquire NGC Token<br/>HTTPS/443, Basic Auth (API key)
    NVAuth-->>NIMCtrl: NGC Bearer Token
    NIMCtrl->>NVAPI: Validate API Key + Fetch Models<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    NVAPI-->>NIMCtrl: Model catalog data
    NIMCtrl->>NVCR: Verify image manifests<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    NVCR-->>NIMCtrl: Manifest OK
    NIMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (runtime data)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    NIMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Template (ServingRuntime)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    NIMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pull Secret (nvcr.io)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    Note over User,NVCR: Flow 3: Gateway Auth Bootstrap

    K8sAPI->>GWCtrl: Watch event: Gateway created
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (TLS)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (Kuadrant)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    Note over User,NVCR: Flow 4: CA Certificate Aggregation

    K8sAPI->>CMCtrl: Watch: odh-trusted-ca-bundle changed
    CMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Read openshift-service-ca.crt<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    CMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create/Update odh-kserve-custom-ca-bundle<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    CMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Delete storage-config (force regen)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
